This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Numerical Analysis (cs.NA), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Symbolic Computation (cs.SC), Software Engineering (cs.SE), or Programming Languages (cs.PL) sub-categories.
